milestones.description: Atapattu and Mahela Jayawardene's 226-run partnership is SL's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 213 between de Silva and Jayasuriya
Atapattu and Mahela Jayawardene's 226-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 213 between Jayasuriya and de Silva
Murali has taken the most five-wicket hauls (4) in ODIs for SL, going past Jayasuriya's record
Tendulkar has scored 75 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Haynes's record
